{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Django/social-login","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"d0a9e3e6-e8a3-54d8-9943-f02032a078d1","html":"<h1 id=\"소셜-로그인-auth\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%86%8C%EC%85%9C-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-auth\" aria-label=\"소셜 로그인 auth permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>소셜 로그인 (Auth)</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>pip install django-allauth</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 로그인 시도할 때 어떤 로직을 사용할것인지</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 통합 User Model</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 고객, 판매자, 관리자 -> User Model -> Group</span>\nAUTHENTICATION_BACKENDS <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.auth.backends.ModelBackend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'allauth.account.auth_backends.AuthenticationBackend'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py / INSTALLED_APPS</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">INSTALLED_APPS <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.admin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.auth'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.contenttypes'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.sessions'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.messages'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.staticfiles'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'board'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 아래내용 추가</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'django.contrib.sites'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'allauth'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'allauth.account'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'allauth.socialaccount'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">'allauth.socialaccount.providers.naver'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># naver</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>settings.py</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">SITE_ID <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>config / urls.py</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">path<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'accounts/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> include<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'allauth.urls'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>python manage.py migrate</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"naver-에-허락맡기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#naver-%EC%97%90-%ED%97%88%EB%9D%BD%EB%A7%A1%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"naver 에 허락맡기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>naver 에 허락맡기</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.naver.com/appinfo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://developers.naver.com/appinfo</a> 접속</li>\n<li>애플리케이션 등록</li>\n<li>python manage.py runserver</li>\n<li>관리자 페이지 설정</li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Django/social-login","tagSlugs":["/tag/social-login/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-05-22","description":"소셜 로그인 (Auth)","tags":["social-login"],"title":"소셜 로그인 (Auth)","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Django/social-login"}}}